{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This script is used to automate the expression of selected notes in REAPER by inserting Control Change (CC) messages into the MIDI data of the notes. The script automatically inserts CC messages based on the length and position of the notes at specified intervals, thereby automating the dynamic expression of the notes. Requires JS_ReaScriptAPI & SWS Extension\par}
}

